Learning Mirah

#i have rvm installed
rvm use jruby

jruby -S gem install mirah


running your mirah code

mirah hello.mirah

compile the mirah code to class
mirahc hello.mirah

#
Parsing...
  hello.mirah
Inferring types...
Compiling...
  hello.mirah
Done!

# creates a file Hello.class

running the compiled code


java Hello
# :) required output and super fast




examples which have worked

mirah fractal.mirah
mirah 